➜宽哥： 《如梦令》—词林正韵
http://www.sohu.com/a/423514529_100115135	56858
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20201009/8192bbb88f724db0abc57b9aed4c233f.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>《如梦令》—词林正韵</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong> 文/宽哥</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">明日凄然别去，永夜万般思绪。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">起坐独无眠，旧物低眉轻诉。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">徐顾，徐顾。长伴高堂福祚。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20201009/132811a267d049bb9ea7c350386414ae.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20201009/c8ed4bfcb79847cb9d9cc349dadf49c3.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
