➜广东诗人小隐：寒露杂诗
http://www.sohu.com/a/423522625_100115135	57022
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20201009/25c1749be2d344bf9e2acef36c8da06c.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>寒露杂诗</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>文/小隐</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">此时花谢了，黄菊始为开。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">竹影摇风径，松梢望月台。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">方知寒露至，复见暮云堆。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">人老多伤事，凉秋鬓更灰。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20201009/3ee4821fa2f04508921a5037986ba791.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>▲<strong>【作者简介】：</strong>小隐，自由职业者，一个游走人间的过客，喜欢用文字与灵魂对话的小女人，左手柴米油盐酱拌醋～右手诗词歌赋花间茶～</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20201009/f4a3bce9c8fd4a16abe9f6fe2fc7dceb.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
