➜广西诗人陈熠明：醉美了情感的青山
http://www.sohu.com/a/423524195_100115135	58025
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>醉美了情感的青山</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>现代诗原创作品·心灵诗幻陈熠明</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20201010/7dbc29944d5a4207ae1c2704ca31bddd.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">(一)</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">你看见了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">看见那云霞里</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">有一烟紫气在静静地萦绕</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>萦绕着那一片</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>翠绿了岁月的青山</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">你悄悄地转身</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">你在清风里悄悄地转身</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>转身走过时光里</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>那一个更迭了青春的流年</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">放不下那一个</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">淡淡地说走了流年的昨天</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>凤凰鸟的歌声在婉转</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>婉转着让那一个花开的季节芳菲成</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">芳菲成那一心</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">又一心点燃了情感的烂漫</p>            <div class="lookall-box">
<div class="lookall-shadow"></div>
